&lt;li&gt;A data science project through &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.northatlantic.tech&quot;&gt;North Atlantic Tech&lt;/a&gt; utilizing Python, Docker, AWS, Redis, GraphQL, Hasura, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
