&lt;p&gt;We used every trick in the book to add a little more polish to this great documentary.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Stargate Origins]]></title><description><![CDATA[I grew up watching all the different Stargate series and it’s actually part of what got me interested in VFX in the first place - so I…]]></description><link>https://jeffhq.com/stargate-origins/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jeffhq.com/stargate-origins/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2018 22:40:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;I grew up watching all the different Stargate series and it’s actually part of what got me interested in VFX in the first place - so I jumped at the opportunity to have my name in the credits when Tom called saying he could use some help.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I really only did one day’s worth of work on this comping in moons, painting out tire-tracks, and some other small things… Plus another day attempting to track a 46 second long shot of sand dunes in &lt;a href=&quot;https://borisfx.com/products/mocha-pro/&quot;&gt;mocha&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Microsoft 12 Days of Deals]]></title><description><![CDATA[Intro Animation  Credits Client: Contend Producer: Seth Josephson Motion Graphics: Jeff Hodges]]></description><link>https://jeffhq.com/microsoft/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jeffhq.com/microsoft/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2017 22:40:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h4&gt;Intro Animation&lt;/h4&gt;
